{"tid":1576990,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［城大人入］又話整連儂隧道？？？","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:09:39.000Z","uid":303452,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0e764aa8b3bb037c644e1759462471cd83ef1e16","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"由開學講到依家<br />\n都冇人真係做嘅？<br />\n個人覺得依家個民主牆起唔到咩大作用<br />\n冇心跟本唔會行埋去睇<br />\n個人覺得時光隧道/3M橋都可以發展<br />\n仲有咩地方都可以提議下<br />\n有冇城大人真係想一齊整？？<br />\n要快啲組隊去整架喇！"},{"pid":"ee280cf72f354fd207118c6d312fa44204d1309c","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a360b0099a44a9448d18d50a84b74ac49be5c3","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bab78e6a4db5d875f669218c7d0545a678417b","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e6d698d8681279f12a184afe0baaa04c288e2d","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4475dbf7b672cdd3d99e49a1def29205f76380","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b385c704e1f906fedf83b11e9a7992a947f5ac6b","tid":1576990,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"開啟新戰線：「天滅中共 平反六四」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正式輸出革命<br />\n<br />\n係大陸人比較多嘅地方，<br />\neg. ifc國歌集會，上水羅湖落馬洲邊境，大學內地生（NDS) 聚腳場合<br />\n<br />\n1）不斷傳播解放軍89六四當年鎮壓市民真相<br />\n<br />\n2）瘋狂播《血染的風采》，播到中共連每日150單程證都唔夠膽放落嚟為止，彭麗媛版本更理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）要將「天滅中共，平反六四」加入為一主要口號，用國語讀更佳<br />\n（如果見到啲廢老藍絲拍片最好叫呢句，啲官媒一定唔夠膽將啲片傳返上大陸，要令佢哋嘅維穩工作白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DutvG-uwDsD8%26list%3DRDutvG-uwDsD8%26start_radio%3D1&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=272ad9f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n也許我告別 將不再回來 你是否理解 你是否明白<br />\n也許我倒下 再不能起來 你是否還要 永久的期待<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n也許我的眼睛 再不能睜開 你是否理解 我沉默的情懷<br />\n也許我長眠 將不能醒來 你是否相信 我化作了山脈<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的土壤裡有我們付出的愛<br />\n<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n如果是這樣 你不要悲哀 共和國的旗幟上有我們血染的風采<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果有人話：「呢啲係鄰國嘅事，我哋顧掂自己香港，爭取真普選先」<br />\n請你哋block Q咗呢啲人，果啲係五毛嚟<br />\n因為而家係鄰國過去咁多年每日每分每秒搞鳩緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n鄰國愈亂，自顧不暇，各省地方勢力掘起，對我哋有利</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4ba5d36945b238ae041678a258e8298c85edb113","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e155337b83f64de9bf2972fb4acd06bed94282","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf670ead50c370f866c2a5a18dcb3beb1cdcd17","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38aaf764316e7fc1e3f1eda0f66debff3d5e53f","tid":1576990,"uid":303452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"